- Apa?

892
01:26:31.032 --> 01:26:33.687
Billy Hodges datang ke pestaku?

893
01:26:34.905 --> 01:26:36.994
Daah, Billy.

894
01:26:40.258 --> 01:26:41.956
- Hai.
- Hai.

